salsa was amazingly good, my husband had to ask what it was and was shocked to hear it was zucchini. I did add the salt slowly to monitor taste. easy and good, I would try it with chicken too, or tacos

Rating: 2
This was a good recipe. I diced the salsa ingredients, but would recommend blending them as the recipe suggests. I would also reduce the amount of salt called for, but overall a healthy and tasty halibut dish.

