Rating: 3
Needing to use up a zucchini, I stumbled on this recipe and just had to give it a try. Lovely, refreshing, and a great change of pace. We kept the extra salsa to scoop up with tortilla chips the next day. Even my mom, who was wary of both halibut and any kind of green sauce, loved it.

Rating: 4
This was delicious. I made it with chicken breasts on the grill pan instead of halibut. I did not skimp on the jalapeño and it was delightfully refreshing on a hot summer evening.

Rating: 3
